# 📊 Business Intelligence Dashboard Suite | Power BI

A comprehensive **Business Intelligence Dashboard Suite** built using **Microsoft Power BI** to transform raw sales data into meaningful business insights. This project focuses on analyzing business performance through interactive dashboards, enabling data-driven decision-making.

---

## 🚀 Project Overview

This repository contains **five interactive Power BI dashboards** developed using the Superstore dataset:

- 📌 Executive Dashboard
- 📈 Sales Analysis Dashboard
- 📦 Product Performance Dashboard
- 👥 Customer Analysis Dashboard
- 💰 Financial Analysis Dashboard

Each dashboard provides unique insights into different aspects of business performance through dynamic visualizations and KPIs.

---

## ✨ Key Features

- Interactive KPI Cards
- Sales & Profit Analysis
- Customer Analytics
- Product Performance Tracking
- Financial Performance Analysis
- Regional Business Insights
- Dynamic Filters & Slicers
- Professional Dashboard Design
- Business Intelligence Reporting

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Microsoft Power BI
- Power Query
- DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)
- Data Modeling
- Superstore Dataset (CSV)

---

## 📊 Dashboards Included

| Dashboard | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| Executive Dashboard | Overall business performance overview |
| Sales Analysis | Sales trends, regions, and category insights |
| Product Performance | Product-wise sales and profitability |
| Customer Analysis | Customer behavior and lifetime value |
| Financial Analysis | Revenue, profit, and financial KPIs |

---

## 📈 Business Insights

This dashboard suite helps answer questions like:

- Which products generate the highest revenue?
- Which regions perform the best?
- Who are the most valuable customers?
- How are sales and profits trending over time?
- Which products require business attention?

